Definition: handsome shrub with showy orange to scarlet or crimson flowers
Example: Florida and West Indies to Mexico and Brazil
Synonyms: scarlet_hamelia, coloradillo, Hamelia_patens, Hamelia_erecta, hamelia, handsome, shrub, with, showy, orange, to, scarlet, or, crimson, flowers, Florida, and, West, Indies, Mexico, Brazil
Category: noun.plant
